               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. DOANE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Did you give him these to take to Mrs. Priddle? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, with the twenty-four pairs of boots.</p>
