                  </hi>. The prisoner did not deliver to me the four pairs of half-boots, the thirteen pairs of ladies' slippers, and the three pairs of childrens shoes—the shoes had not been ordered by me, only the boots—he showed me some shoes, but I immediately declined taking them—he put them into his basket and took them away.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
